<h4 id="bespoke-solutions">Bespoke Solutions</h4>
<ul>
  <li>SLKone worked with leadership to define objectives, processes, and desired templates</li>
  <li>Defined line item aggregation to produce meaningful finance budgets</li>
  <li>Created financial estimates to capture bottoms up estimate from a portfolio of &gt;50 locations</li>
  <li>Developed a 3-Statement Budget model, ultimately approved by equity sponsor and lender</li>
  <li>Documented new budget process and transitioned new budget model to finance team</li>
  <li>Created a budget vs. actuals reporting suite, which automated variance analysis</li>
</ul>

